    "Id": "chassisdef_cockroach_CRH-4H2",
    "Name": "Cockroach",
    "Details": "The CRH-4H2 builds directly on the CRH-4H, upgrading all three Medium Lasers to Medium Pulse Lasers and adding a fourth in the center torso for substantially improved close-range accuracy and output. An Advanced Targeting Computer and additional energy and heat tracking systems further sharpen its weapons' effectiveness, supported by extra heat sinks in both arms. To accommodate this expanded and refined arsenal, the CRH-4H2 sacrifices its jump jets entirely — a trade-off that grounds the design but leaves its renowned armor and defensive systems fully intact.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Reinforced Structure</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.14</color></b>",
    "Icon": "uixTxrIcon_ironclad"
